PrecisAmendments to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS that increase the capital cost allowance rate for manufacturing and processing assets from 25% to 30% and allow corporations that process ore extracted from a source outside Canada to qualify for the capital cost allowance.

precis:
Amendments to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS that increase the capital cost
allowance rate for manufacturing and processing assets from 25% to 30%
and allow corporations that process ore extracted from a source outside
Canada to qualify for the capital cost allowance.
